The paper proposes a method for meta-learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The method is applicable to various tasks such as regression, classification, and reinforcement learning, indicating that it could fall under multiple sub-categories. Based on the content of the paper, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.RO (Robotics), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
